---
title: Avocado, Parmesan & Rocket Salad with Almonds & Balsamic Glaze | Serves 2
description: The classic pairing of greens and Parmesan gets an upgrade with the addition of roasted almonds, cucumber,
avocado and parsley. Finish it off with a drizzle of syrupy balsamic glaze.
